<HEAD><TITLE>

On Information Warfare: R.L. DiNardo and Daniel J. Hughes

</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffFF">


<!-- Header/Nav-Bar Table -------------------------------------------->

<table width=580 border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
