<a href="http://www.whitehouse.gov">http://www.whitehouse.gov</a><BR>
(NEW: U.S. Congress Internet Caucus<BR>
<a href="http://www.house.gov/white/internet_caucus/netcauc.html">http://www.house.gov/white/internet_caucus/netcauc.html</a><BR>
  <BR>
10.  INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT COOPERATION<BR>
<a href="http://www.alcazar.com/wwwvl_idc/index.html">http://www.alcazar.com/wwwvl_idc/index.html</a><BR>
