	National Computer Security Association <a href="www.ncsa.com">(www.ncsa.com)</a><BR>
	Winn Schwartau's Infowar.Com <a href="www.infowar.com">(www.infowar.com)</a><BR>
	Robert Steele's OSS, Inc. <a href="www.oss.net">(www.oss.net)</a><BR>
